<br>
--25 secs into fight--<br>
<br>
Unedjucated Guildie: He is in the wall back the pets off NOW!!<br>
Me: Cool backing off.<br>
<br>
--35 secs into fight--<br>
<br>
Unedjucated Guildie: Mulk back off your %^&amp;*ing pet!!<br>
Me: Yo guys I already did he is right here.<br>
Other Unedjucated Guildie tells you: Get that dam hammers off Vindy.<br>
Me SHOUTs: Invis the clerics so the pet will die.<br>
Most of Guild: Why would we invis the clerics back off your hammers.<br>
