It still amazes me sometimes how much some ppl know NOTHING about other classes. I don't really play any others, but at least I am familiar with things, and I READ patch messages.(another peeve of mine.) <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"> Wildet Manaweaver<br>
